subject: Re: Director, General Investigatio
body:
Hello Mrs. Kristalina Georgieva,

Thank you for reaching out to me. I'm surprised to hear about this package, as I wasn't expecting anything. Could you please provide more details about it? What is the content of the box? And how did Mr. Larry Peter Wilson come into possession of it?

I'm sorry to hear about his accident and hope he's doing well now.

Looking forward to hearing from you soon.

Best wishes,
Debra
